{"tid":1430621,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[Fact Check咗未?] 警總有可能爆發手足口病嗎?","createTime":"2019-08-07T19:26:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T20:36:05.000Z","uid":149534,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a3c5ebd3893068d2fd41ac7a3b1673ed97b52b","tid":1430621,"uid":149534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:26:50.000Z","msg":"手足口病通常在兒童之間傳播, 成人感染率極低.<br />\n而大家都睇漏眼既一點係......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來黑警唔係人, 係畜牲,<br />\n所以係不會爆發手足口病 (Hand, foot, and mouth disease), <br />\n只會傳染口蹄疫 (foot-and-mouth disease).<br />\n結論: 警總爆發手足口病係Fake News, 大家千奇唔好炒車, 要爆都係爆口蹄疫啦.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"152b14a45f8c8a080d93db3b3fb5ec15fb4d16b3","tid":1430621,"uid":149534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:28:26.000Z","msg":"上次非洲豬瘟政府殺豬殺得咁快, 如市民發現有口蹄疫既畜牲要盡快通知漁護署撲殺啊."},{"pid":"39f46cd6a9471a9de27ba119aa070640cc0bb859","tid":1430621,"uid":149534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:36:05.000Z","msg":"警總口蹄疫爆發成因分析:<br />\n<br />\n1. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(藍衫長時間被白衫上級奴役)<br />\n<br />\n2. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (已經停止發放OT補水, 散仔冇錢開飯)<br />\n<br />\n3. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (進食太多被加料飯盒同凍撚水)<br />\n<br />\n4. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (聞得太多過期催淚煙係自己身邊爆開)<br />\n<br />\n5. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (換黑衫嫁禍勇武, 入戲太深引致精神失常)<br />\n<br />\n6. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三二<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (到現場發現示威者be water曬, 谷到一肚火)<br />\n<br />\n7. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (被困警署想訓點知俾同袍啲槍聲吵醒)<br />\n<br />\n8. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (經常俾鐳射槍射同被掟嘢)<br />\n<br />\n9. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (每日都要係記者會上出醜)<br />\n<br />\n黑警的工作環境十分惡劣, 容易導致疾病蔓延. <br />\n口蹄疫預防勝於撲殺, 政府應儘早<del>清算</del>清洗警務處以防病菌散播."}]}